- Support for selecting packages by provided dependencies.
- Show download size before starting fetching.
- Make slack-site default priority be 100 or so.
- Remove support for channel descriptions.
- Do not remove packages when PackageManager.commit() returns
  with error.
- Clean stdin buffer before asking for user input.
- Write lock scheme to avoid running multiple transactions
  at the same time, and multiple channel updates at the same
  time.
